name: Aspx-photoupload
tagline: webform snippet for asp.net - implement a simple photo uploader for SQL Server
body:
### Welcome to GitHub Pages.
This is a simple file uploader for .net and SQL Server

```
Open solution file with Visual Studio 2010 Web Express
Click "Default2.aspx" to get start 
```

![Snapshot](https://raw.github.com/ilovejs/aspx-photoupload/master/snapshot.jpg)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
